    "title": "心を掴んで離さない、その名は――",
    "enTitle": "Capturing Their Hearts, The Name Is――",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "キュキュ～☆　劇場版アニメ『キューまると海の王国』、\nただいま絶賛公開中よ！",
            "enText": "Kyukyu～☆ The Anime movie 『Kyumaru and the \nSeaside Kingdom』 is airing to rave reviews!",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 251,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": 662889540871405842
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7973683343156779018,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "海で迷子になったキューまると仲間たち、\nそこで訪れる新たな出会い――みんなも気になるわよね？",
            "enText": "After Kyumaru and his friends are lost at sea, they go on a \nbrand new adventure――Everyone, you're all dying to know more, right?",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 270,
            "voiceIdx": 1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 130,
                    "pathId": -8707913686163811882
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 16,
                    "pathId": -8926723651021957303
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5228153113484928217,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "愛と勇気の大冒険！\nアイと一緒に、劇場で楽しみましょう♪",
            "enText": "A grand adventure full of love and courage! \nTogether with Ai, we'll have a wonderful time at the theater♪",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 227,
            "voiceIdx": 2,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 43,
                    "pathId": -641712470824610995
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -4012337109813658191
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6938993194171127959,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ミーハーなウマ娘A",
            "enName": "Trendy Uma Musume A",
            "jpText": "わっ、あれって本物だよね！？\nアイちゃんかわいい！　オーラすご～い！",
            "enText": "Wah, that's really her, isn't it!? \nAi-chan is so cute! Her aura is crazy～!",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 227,
            "voiceIdx": 3,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 25,
                    "pathId": 8628484310012129935
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 188,
                    "pathId": 6246264410759953083
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 136,
                    "pathId": -7710141782145374719
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7780108084845017663,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ミーハーなウマ娘B",
            "enName": "Trendy Uma Musume B",
            "jpText": "アイちゃーん、CM見たよ～！\n私も映画、観にいきたくなっちゃった！！",
            "enText": "Ai-chan, we saw that CM～! \nIt made me want to watch the movie too!!",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 191,
            "voiceIdx": 4,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 240,
                    "pathId": 7546546493396663209
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 191,
                    "pathId": -2890309701958030884
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1098135006964660262,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "ふふっ、ありがとう！　これからも応援よろしくね！",
            "enText": "Fufuu, thank you! I hope you'll keep cheering me on!",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 132,
            "voiceIdx": 5,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 131,
                    "pathId": 28615542795630229
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 462170482734536821
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 200400233105443112,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "以前、キューまる人形をかけて共に挑んだクイズ。その様子が、\n視察中の役員の目に留まり、映画のCMに起用されたのだが――",
            "enText": "A little while ago we won a pair of Kyumaru dolls from \na quiz contest. This caught the eye of a top level \nexecutive, and they asked her to help promote the movie――",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 121,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "あちこちで声をかけられて気が休まらないな",
                    "enText": "Must be hard to relax with all that attention",
                    "nextBlock": 8
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "あちこちで声をかけられて気が休まらないね",
                    "enText": "Must be hard to relax with all that attention",
                    "nextBlock": 8
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": 5983337693844860648
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1787070036872554003,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "わたしは嬉しいわよ？\n注目も期待も、されればされるほど燃えるもの。",
            "enText": "I'm happy though? \nThe more attention and expectations, the more fired up I get.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 209,
            "voiceIdx": 6,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 180,
                    "pathId": -8602284335894049130
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": 7084240442561060436
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1978201550867350097,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "？？？",
            "enName": "???",
            "jpText": "ああ、なんて頼もしい言葉だ！\nやはりお願いするならあなたしかいない……！",
            "enText": "Aah, what reliable words! \nReally, if I had to ask anyone, it would have to be you……!",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 203,
            "voiceIdx": 7,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 290,
                    "pathId": -5494859220812463733
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 281,
                    "pathId": -1352090800995333450
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -940320861315246672,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "あら？　えっと……初めまして。貴方は？",
            "enText": "Oh? Ummm……nice to meet you. You are?",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 140,
            "voiceIdx": 8,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 94,
                    "pathId": -295196959760274598
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 24,
                    "pathId": 3096296776860653949
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1004493860631355949,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "夏祭り運営の男性",
            "enName": "Summer Festival Planner",
            "jpText": "ああっ私、この地域の夏祭りの運営をしておりまして……\nこういう者です。",
            "enText": "Aah, I'm the one in charge of handling the Summer Festival here…… \nHere's my card.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 203,
            "voiceIdx": 9,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 214,
                    "pathId": 4356805565749819388
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 115,
                    "pathId": -6642926014898516064
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8006855904288236414,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "夏祭り運営の男性",
            "enName": "Summer Festival Planner",
            "jpText": "実は、週末の夏祭りライブに出ていただくことになっていた\nアイドルの子が、体調を崩してしまって――",
            "enText": "The truth is, the idol we were planning to have \nperform for the Live next week ended up falling ill――",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 260,
            "voiceIdx": 10,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 327,
                    "pathId": 9191754337747265320
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 15,
                    "pathId": -4790350150186379222
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3321517129914616907,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "夏祭り運営の男性",
            "enName": "Summer Festival Planner",
            "jpText": "最近、CM出演で人気上昇中のアイさんに、\nぜひともご出演願えないかと……！　お願いしますっ！",
            "enText": "And suddenly Ai-san, who's been getting popular \nrecently makes an appearance, so we would really \nlike to ask her to participate……! I beg of you!",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 282,
            "voiceIdx": 11,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 293,
                    "pathId": 7076684537460700264
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3768492041821708725,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "夏祭りライブの代役、ということですよね？\n――素敵なお申し出、ありがとうございます。楽しそうですね！",
            "enText": "So a substitute for the Summer Live, right? \n――Thank you for the wonderful opportunity. It sounds fun!",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 258,
            "voiceIdx": 12,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 209,
                    "pathId": 2604083600319413258
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": 5473632490164324623
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7782443056099859485,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "とはいえ、今はウマ娘たちにとって大事な夏合宿中。\n急な依頼で負担も大きいが――",
            "enText": "That said, the Uma Musume were in the middle of their really important \nsummer training camp. The sudden request would be a heavy burden――",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 132,
                    "pathId": -5454570556123949518
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -472555632748375040,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "ねっ、トレーナー！　お話、受けてもいいかしら？",
            "enText": "Hey, Trainer! Is it okay if I accept?",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 119,
            "voiceIdx": 13,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "――うん！やってみようか！",
                    "enText": "――Yeah! Let's give it a shot!",
                    "nextBlock": 17
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -8950613962802964652
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -605925899343869206
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8476172352025707675,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "その強く輝く瞳を、止められない――いや、止めたくはなかった。\n彼女を最大限サポートしよう。そう決めたのは一瞬だった。",
            "enText": "When she looked at me with those bright eyes, I couldn't stop her―― \nNo, I didn't want to. It only took a moment to decide that.",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 120,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 176,
                    "pathId": -7370718189399406175
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": -5719996786707749736
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8052613028222828188,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "はっ、はっ……。トレーナーの改良メニュー、いい感じね！\nでも、もっと負荷をかけてもいいのよ？",
            "enText": "Haa, haa…… Trainer, the improved menu feels just right! \nBut, you can make it harder you know?",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 300,
            "voiceIdx": 14,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 25,
                    "pathId": -4932446733054433007
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 203,
                    "pathId": 6268934171895531642
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 266293035964904974,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "夜遅くまで練っていたやつ、あるんでしょ？\nどうせなら全部やっちゃいましょう！",
            "enText": "You have that one you were working on late in to the night, \ndon't you? Might as well do all of it, don't you think?",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 172,
            "voiceIdx": 15,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "知っていたのか……じゃあやろう！",
                    "enText": "You saw that, huh……Okay, let's do it!",
                    "nextBlock": 20
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "知っていたんだ……じゃあやろう！",
                    "enText": "You saw that, huh……Okay, let's do it!",
                    "nextBlock": 20
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": -4556221177412452733
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6986533675116666979,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "ええ！　大事な夏合宿、悔いのないように鍛えないと！",
            "enText": "Yeah! It's our important summer training camp, \nso we have to train so that we don't have any regrets!",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 169,
            "voiceIdx": 16,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 98,
                    "pathId": 3023919714487687800
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": 8151774395248991029
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6907046508365152232,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "あ～あ～あ～あ～あ～♪",
            "enText": "Ah～ah～ah～ah～ah～♪",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 120,
            "voiceIdx": 17,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -7864450646809185247
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 174,
                    "pathId": 407734369850733979
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7552458083022334674,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "見晴らしのいい場所で声を出すのって、気持ちいいわね。\n気分もスカッとするし、最高！",
            "enText": "It feels really nice to be able to sing out loud in such \na scenic place. It's really refreshing, it's the best!",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 237,
            "voiceIdx": 18,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 166,
                    "pathId": 9075733820275765457
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": -4981942608107444563
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7699451177003285301,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "ねえ、貴方も歌ってみない？\nコーラスありで練習したいわ。",
            "enText": "Hey, how about trying to sing too? \nIt has a chorus that I want to practice too.",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 141,
            "voiceIdx": 19,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 192,
                    "pathId": -5956158779147905535
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 171,
                    "pathId": -8304175075187772141
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3564671152700992910,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "正直、若干恥ずかしい。アーモンドアイに\n満足してもらえるコーラスができるかわからないが――",
            "enText": "To be honest, it was a little embarrassing for me. I didn't know if \nI could sing a chorus that would match well with Almond Eye, but――",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 103,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "れ、練習なら……とことん付き合うよ！！",
                    "enText": "I-if it's practice……then I'm in!!",
                    "nextBlock": 25
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 114,
                    "pathId": 6480199209231999926
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 171,
                    "pathId": 7778176874138124196
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7624945941351099832,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "そうこなくっちゃ。じゃあ、いってみましょうか！\n――あこがれの地へ～♪",
            "enText": "That's what I want to hear. Then, let's give it a shot! \n――To that place that seemed so far～♪",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 291,
            "voiceIdx": 20,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "勇気すこし借りて",
                    "enText": "With a little push on the back",
                    "nextBlock": 26
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 270,
                    "pathId": -1097470223484922858
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 5615893500912524288
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4332589094141044166,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "語り合ったMEMORY～♪",
            "enText": "All of our shared memories～♪",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 145,
            "voiceIdx": 21,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "二度と来ない今を",
                    "enText": "Never let the moment slip away",
                    "nextBlock": 27
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 302,
                    "pathId": -6273524287181456892
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6536320173842017684,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "もう　ドキドキもトキメキも\n抑えられない　たまんない　熱いハラハラが止まらな～い♪",
            "enText": "On this beating of my heart, fluttering with joy \nCan't keep it down, no can't hold it back \nRush of heat and passion, it's not gonna stop～♪",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 315,
            "voiceIdx": 22,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 204,
                    "pathId": -8785078577545419775
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 214,
                    "pathId": -8388479345556158366
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2239012192070889115,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "キ　ミ　と　！",
            "enText": "YOU AND I!",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 63,
            "voiceIdx": 23,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 59,
                    "pathId": 3606292768001025691
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 23,
                    "pathId": -3859426391515256615
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1249435157009048095,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "夏合宿とライブの準備――\nどちらも手を抜かずに、ふたりで全力で駆け抜けていく。",
            "enText": "Summer training camp and preparations for that live performance―― \nWe weren't holding back on either. Together we were giving our all.",
            "nextBlock": 30,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 178,
                    "pathId": 3955391352478086267
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7189786830175394840,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "はああああああああっ！！",
            "enText": "Haaaaaaaaa!!",
            "nextBlock": 31,
            "origClipLength": 50,
            "voiceIdx": 24,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": 2562802293104383405
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3356174176699875480,
            "blockIdx": 30
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "あ、トレーナー！　水分補給なら抜かりないわよ？\nきゅうりとスポドリでばっちり！",
            "enText": "Ah, Trainer! When it comes to hydration, I'm already on top of it. \nWith some cucumber and sports drinks, I'm all good!",
            "nextBlock": 32,
            "origClipLength": 227,
            "voiceIdx": 25,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "さすがだな、熱中症には気をつけないと",
                    "enText": "Good, just watch out for heatstroke",
                    "nextBlock": 32
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "さすがだね、熱中症には気をつけないと",
                    "enText": "Good, just watch out for heatstroke",
                    "nextBlock": 32
                }
            ],
